column5: We need four more people to join to even up the teams.  It won't be fair to all teams if we put the four we have ready to join  on a team.  This will leave four teams with one less team member, and I'm sure that will not go over well  So please, anyone remotely interested in this fun tourney, please sign up.  First 4 are in!!  Thanks a bunch!!!!  Joey
Added my name to the sign up list Joey...
Great, thanks Westarmrider, Now we need 3 and we're good to go!!!
I want in...take a pic submit it with the OFC team name right?
Sure put me down. Guess I better keep a camera with me when I go out.
Yup, you got it, okay, 1 more please
ok sign me up if you still need one more joey
Whooo-hooo. That makes up the 4 last entries. Way to step up guys. What took you so friggen long?
Sweet, thanks guys, okay, we're done then, let the games begin
how do I find out my team? Been searching I can't find it?

The new sign ups are as follows:  RoaringDanSeavey - team 1 Reelinrolly - team 2 Jen - team 3 Trouty - team 4 Westarmraider - team 5 Tightline - team 6 Gotfish - team 7 Rickster - team 8   Also, Captains, please remember to PM me your team names please, thank you!!  Joey
